TaperWarp Icon & Mascot Pack
============================

Contents
--------
01_App_Icons
  - 1024 px master PNG
  - standard PNG sizes from 16 px through 1024 px
  - multi-resolution Windows .ico
  - macOS .icns, when supported by the image encoder

02_Mascot
  - full-body transparent mascot
  - circular avatar
  - one-color mascot
  - sticker mascot

03_Logos
  - logo lockup
  - TaperWarp wordmark

04_UI_Assets
  - light and dark square badges
  - cone-only graphic
  - wrap arrow
  - cone favicon graphic
  - loading spinner

05_Marketing
  - introduction card
  - social banner

Notes
-----
- The worm/easter-egg character has been intentionally excluded.
- Standalone artwork uses transparent PNG backgrounds where practical.
- Cards, badges, and banners retain their designed backgrounds.
- These files were separated from the generated raster asset sheet. They are PNG/raster artwork, not true editable vector SVG files.
- Some large files are upscaled from the source sheet, so they are appropriate for app/UI use but not ideal for very large-format printing.
